{"tid":2284183,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"YG財報公開「明年要推新女團」！BIGBANG回歸日程也曝光","createTime":"2020-11-13T05:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T07:25:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0cfdbc5a3f92f1c9e7daac9913a0dfc6241dbb","tid":2284183,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"南韓三大經紀公司之一的YG娛樂，最新財報預測被流出，也意外透露了所屬藝人動向。其中揭示了YG娛樂預定明年會推新女團，將是繼BLACKPINK之後，睽違5年再推女團；而眾所矚目的BIGBANG動向，回歸日程也曝光了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5267/d5267152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5267%2Fd5267152.jpg&h=ec19de7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲YG財報洩漏BIGBANG回歸動向。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK、BIGBANG臉書）<br />\n<br />\n根據一份「Hana金融投資」昨（12）日流出的YG財報，內容提及YG今年下半年的的營業利潤可達100億韓圜（約台幣2.6億），其中BLACKPINK專輯大賣，成為首位銷售超過100萬張的南韓女團，而新人男團TREASURE從出道至今則賣出25萬張，也算是水準之上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5267/d5267153.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5267%2Fd5267153.jpg&h=20b3dee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲YG財報公開「明年要推新女團」。（圖／翻攝自Hana金融投資）<br />\n<br />\n而分析報告中更發現，YG娛樂將繼今年推出男團之後，計畫於明年推出新女團，另外WINNER兩名尚未入伍的成員昇潤與MINO也將當兵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5267/e5267154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5267%2Fe5267154.jpg&h=938d0c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲分析員分析BIGBANG可能明年上半年有望回歸。（圖／翻攝自Hana金融投資）<br />\n<br />\n此外分析報告也預測，若是能順利開展世界巡迴演唱會，BIGBANG一年可吸引超過百萬名觀眾，2022年可創造600億韓圜（約台幣15.6億）的營業利潤，分析員更補充道，「若依據原計畫能展開線上巡迴演唱會的話，BIGBANG可能將於明年上半年回歸樂壇」。"},{"pid":"e470b1f87c04a72990cdfaa095f88a003f3ea929","tid":2284183,"uid":92194,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:59:33.000Z","msg":"賺幾千萬港紙都幾少下"},{"pid":"82b2a47e12e858b096c0110c98eb9dea09044959","tid":2284183,"uid":256796,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"新團同BP一齊屌打Twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ba658738909b5dfb003b2e2bc66f4c847dfa16","tid":2284183,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c87afec8382f5c187af90be13669a3530a4f78","tid":2284183,"uid":377355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"新團vs aespa<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7187d190d2e3f360ea792508ac3c070a5944aa1","tid":2284183,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"82b2a47e12e858b096c0110c98eb9dea09044959","tid":2284183,"uid":256796,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"新團同BP一齊屌打Twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"TWICE殺晒全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347e4ad7df7de36dc34ddd0262ce2f58d9b71d27","tid":2284183,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25ba658738909b5dfb003b2e2bc66f4c847dfa16","tid":2284183,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"G Danger<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da8165105ed9c97943a760bcf497bc6e6bdd197","tid":2284183,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:07:0